2007-10-26  Benoit Sigoure  <tsuna@lrde.epita.fr>

	Don't use Boost.Filesystem in the kernel.
	libboost_filesystem is not available on Aibo, so we can't use it in
	the kernel.
	* include/kernel/userver.hh,
	* src/Makefile.am,
	* src/userver.cc: Revert the changes done at r1828 and r1838.

