2007-10-19  Akim Demaille  <akim@lrde.epita.fr>

	<< for tags.
	This patch is a rough implementation of << for channels.
	It actually makes << and : both usable for both tags and
	channels.  If someone wants to improve this, go ahead.
	* src/parser/bison/ugrammar.y (<<, >>): New tokens.
	(YYSTYPE::is_colon, colon_or_ltlt): New.
	* src/parser/bison/utoken.l (<<, >>): New tokens.
	Fix the catch-all rule to be active for all the start conditions
	(fixes a Flex warning).

